      <title>交易员纷纷买入廉价泰晤士水务债券以押注重组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/traders-pile-into-cheap-thames-water-bonds-on-restructuring-bet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，基金经理正在买入远低于面值的泰晤士水务债券，并押注潜在重组带来的任何削减都不会像目前交易水平所显示的那样痛苦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/traders-pile-into-cheap-thames-water-bonds-on-restructuring-bet</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 11:16:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
