      <title>收视率下降的危险增加了马克龙的预算压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/danger-of-a-ratings-hit-turns-up-the-budget-pressure-for-macron</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国信用评级下调的危险加剧了法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 面临的挑战，因为他被迫在 6 月欧盟选举前夕调整预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/danger-of-a-ratings-hit-turns-up-the-budget-pressure-for-macron</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 11:13:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
