      <title>摩根大通分析师称自 2015 年以来首次购买玛莎百货股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/jpmorgan-analysts-say-buy-m-s-shares-for-first-time-since-2015</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司分析师转而看好马莎百货。英国零售商 Spencer Group Plc 近十年来首次赢得服装市场份额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/jpmorgan-analysts-say-buy-m-s-shares-for-first-time-since-2015</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 11:10:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国村镇银行对超长期债券投资发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/china-s-rural-banks-warned-about-ultra-long-bond-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国多个地区的村镇银行已被建议限制超长期主权债券的投资，此举可能会导致这些证券近期的涨势回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/china-s-rural-banks-warned-about-ultra-long-bond-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 11:05:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯袭击乌克兰天然气储存基地，导致价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/russia-attacks-ukraine-gas-storage-sites-driving-prices-higher</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯周四袭击了乌克兰的两个地下天然气储存设施，推高了欧洲的油价，并再次提醒人们该国的能源基础设施面临威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/russia-attacks-ukraine-gas-storage-sites-driving-prices-higher</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 10:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安联经济学家苏布兰谈美联储、欧洲央行降息和油价影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-11/a-10-rise-in-oil-would-raise-european-inflation-by-1-2-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安联首席经济学家 Ludovic Subran 预计欧洲央行今年将降息 50 个基点 - 然而，石油价格上涨可能会使央行的情况变得复杂，并削弱对美联储降息的预期。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-11/a-10-rise-in-oil-would-raise-european-inflation-by-1-2-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 10:09:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国期货、债券因降息希望减弱而下滑：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股指期货和债券小幅走低，预示着华尔街将进一步下跌，因为顽固的通胀迫使投资者降低对美联储降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 22:45:34 GMT</pubDate>
